<div class="accordion-heading"><a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapsemaintwo">
		<i class="icon-star"></i>
		<h3>Minutes of SAC Meeting held on 18th September 2012:</h3></a>
</div> <!-- /widget-header -->
</div>
</div>
<div class="widget-content">
<div id="collapsemaintwo" class="collapse"><div class="accordion-inner">
The Dean (Students) spoke about the importance of redressal mechanisms in the institute.<br>
The need for students to clarify their issues via proper channels was emphasized upon.<br>
He also briefed about the processes involved in the selection of messes for the past academic year and the present year. <br><br>
A representative from MITr will be made a special invitee to SAC meetings.<br><br>
Prakash Reddy Putta has been selected as the 'Institute Film Club Student Head'.<br><br>
A Female Security committee has been formed comprising the Speaker SAC, SGS, RAS, the general secretaries of Sharavati and Sarayu and volunteers.<br><br>
		
		<div class="accordion" id="accordion2">
				<div class="accordion-group">
						<div class="accordion-heading">
								<a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseSix">
										Regarding Students Facilities
								</a>
						</div>
						<div id="collapseSix" class="accordion-body collapse">
								<div class="accordion-inner"><ul>
<li>All India Travel Agency outlet at Gurunath shall be removed and replaced with a Railway Tatkal Counter</li>
<li>seating capacity at SFC will be increased , Engineering Unit has already initiated the works.</li>
<li>Engineering Unit has initiated repairs works for Road & Parking lights at Himalaya.</li>
<li>New items will be added in GFC and also negotiation of prices will be done in the next two weeks</li>
<li>Barbecue section will be opened in Zaitoon</li>
<li>Hostel Delivery will start from Zaitoon & Gurunath soon.</li>
<li>A new Complex is planned near the girl's hostels with facilities for stationery/ General Items, cycle repair, Beauty Parlour, 24 Hour Canteen etc.</li>
<li>a 24 hour canteen near office of hostel management will be opened within the next one and a half month.</li>
<li>24 Hour Internet facility during examination period.</li>
<li>Free Photocopy facility for students , IIT Madras</li></ul>
								</div>
						</div>
				</div><!--accordion-group-->
				<div class="accordion-group">
						<div class="accordion-heading">
								<a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseSeven">
										Power Laundry
								</a>
						</div>
						<div id="collapseSeven" class="accordion-body collapse">
								<div class="accordion-inner"><ul>
<li>Work of a power laundry service will be started by 27th September,2012 (Tentatively).</li>
<li>Laundry operations will start at Brahmaputra Hostel basement after rainy season. Till then, It will be operated from outside, while distribution & ironing would be operated from brahmaputra basement.</li></ul>
								</div>
						</div>
				</div><!--accordion-group-->
				<div class="accordion-group">
						<div class="accordion-heading">
								<a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseEight">
										 Cycle Sharing System is being looked into where in
								</a>
						</div>
						<div id="collapseEight" class="accordion-body collapse">
								<div class="accordion-inner"><ul><li>Cycle would be maintained by outside vendor.</li>
<li>Students can borrow cycles from different points of the institute.</li>
<li>Charges will be based on the duration for which cycle is borrowed and the type of cycle borrowed</li></ul>
								</div>
						</div>
				</div><!--accordion-group-->
				<div class="accordion-group">
						<div class="accordion-heading">
								<a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseNine">
										Disaster Management Committee:
								</a>
						</div>
						<div id="collapseNine" class="accordion-body collapse">
								<div class="accordion-inner"><ul>
<li>A committee has been formulated.</li>
<li>Conducting workshops on fire drills & Emergency medical care till semester. </li>
<li>Analyzing disaster management plan for bigger venues like OAT, SAC etc</li></ul>				</div>
						</div>
				</div><!--accordion-group-->
