 Institute Web-ops and Mob-Ops team has been formed. It shall help in:
								</a>
						</div>
						<div id="collapseTen" class="accordion-body collapse">
								<div class="accordion-inner">
<ul><li>A better webpage design for the institute website</li>
<li>Institute mob-ops team for mobile application for handy and easy access to necessary information of the institute</li></ul>
								</div>
						</div>
				</div><!--accordion-group-->
				
