								<div class="accordion-inner"><ul>
<li>An external party has been appointed to monitor the mess</li>
<li>New items requested in the food court will be added soon.</li>
<li>The following changes are being proposed in mess (Approved by SAC Members)</li>
<li>Proposal for Bio metric fingerprint check to enter the mess</li>
<li>Using Student ID card for extras and</li>
<li>Online mess account</li></ul>			</div>
