Regarding Slow Internet:
								</a>
						</div>
						<div id="collapseTwelve" class="accordion-body collapse">
								<div class="accordion-inner">Prof. Nitin Chandrachoodan addressed the students. He stated that<ul>
<li>Problem was not due to bandwidth limitation</li>
<li>Also Wi-Fi replacements are planned in current Wi-Fi locations</li>
<li>A committee has been formulated to address students’ issues with regard to Hostel Management Staff</li>
<li>Procedure to use Hostel student welfare fund was explained by HAS & SGS.</li>
