A monthly research newsletter was brought out, to enable the passage of information/news among and between the research scholars. It is being uploaded in the official website of T5E, <a href="http://students.iitm.ac.in/thefifthestate/links/renews/">http://students.iitm.ac.in/thefifthestate/links/renews/</a>, under the independent publications.
