						<div class="accordion-heading">
								<a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2" href="#collapseFourteen">
IITM Alumni Mentor Pilot Project: 					</a>
						</div>
						<div id="collapseFourteen" class="accordion-body collapse">
								<div class="accordion-inner">A pilot project was initiated in coordination with IITMAA where students having difficulties in academics or in choosing career options are put in contact with IITM Alumni, who help them in due course. Huge response with 15 requests in 3 hrs and registration had to be closed in 3 hrs. As it was first come first served and we were planning to take only 4 students for the project. It will be restarted once the official website is launched.
								</div>
						</div>
				</div><!--accordion-group-->
